{"tid":1526032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家千祈唔好做","createTime":"2019-09-01T04:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:02:51.000Z","uid":72455,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ae65ecf524127b91b86ac7a608047a17daea8934","tid":1526032,"uid":72455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"而加警察雖然極醜惡 但千祈唔好對付啲休班警員 <br />\n休班警會落單 正所謂明人不做暗事，警察呢啲正義之仕都會扮示威者 所以我地千祈唔好學，唔好對付休班警員，如果捉一個休班警員再要求政府對話就更加唔好唔好啦，人地警察都係打份工姐，我地一定要做良好市民呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b326e968205b1e8e6780032d139b5b06499a0c","tid":1526032,"uid":72455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:00:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"249a873dbeee6585840cc0b4642b5f855db965e3","tid":1526032,"uid":72455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f04377953aaaadc3b8f7335ffebec27c2063485","tid":1526032,"uid":72455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"要做好市民呀"},{"pid":"2d575bfbeedbca45e6af34e7a749e5bdebb0a3b1","tid":1526032,"uid":72455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15a79d7ef28a8529fd2742f33ef6585e6c7b6152","tid":1526032,"uid":72455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:02:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3abb8d5f6a45f0197af22511d21a80fba099050","tid":1526032,"uid":6561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2Xw%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=1eb5b011\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}